      "writtenOn": "2018-01-08T19:28:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think that resize is guaranteed to free the memory.  shrink_to_fit may help, but that\u0027s also not guaranteed.\n\nThe pattern I\u0027ve used before to guarantee it is mPlaybackCommands.swap(std::vector\u003cTargetCommand\u003e());",
