      "writtenOn": "2018-01-08T20:50:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "actually, swap() needs an l-value reference, so it is std::vector\u003cTargetCommand\u003e().swap(mPlaybackCommands);\nor decltype(mPlaybackCommands){}.swap(mPlaybackCommands) if you don\u0027t want to repeat the type twice",
